title: A+ Guide to Managing & Maintaining Your PC, 8th Edition
description:
2013 | ISBN: 1133135080, 1285193164 | English | 1344 pages | PDF | 76.80 MB

This step-by-step, highly visual text provides a comprehensive introduction to managing and maintaining computer hardware and software. 

Written by best-selling author and educator Jean Andrews, A+ GUIDE TO MANAGING AND MAINTAINING YOUR PC closely integrates the CompTIAA+ Exam objectives to prepare you for the 220-801 and 220-802 certification exams.
